In a decent family, a 17-year-old daughter is pregnant. Everyone is terrified, they can't find a place for themselves. The father screams like a victim:
- I will definitely kill him!
A sports car stops at the house, a man got out of it and said to his father:
- I am married and I will not leave my family. But at the same time, I will not leave your daughter either. When she gives birth... if she gives birth, she will receive a small combine and $ 10 million, but if she has an abortion or has a miscarriage...
the father interrupts without listening to the rest:
- Then you fuck her again!
